=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/f6b6f01e5537abd138a787e9455bdab7.avif?t=1756013880\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/80cfe637c65dd9532e7be1d3d79c3f57.poster.avif?t=1756013880\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/80cfe637c65dd9532e7be1d3d79c3f57.webm?t=1756013880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/80cfe637c65dd9532e7be1d3d79c3f57.mp4?t=1756013880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>你可以在商店花光你的每一分钱，把背包填充得满满当当！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/430d11aa5b33b73bbce6f97fca0445fc.avif?t=1756013880\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/83686f52bdb7e2afff2a4d6403637190.poster.avif?t=1756013880\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/83686f52bdb7e2afff2a4d6403637190.webm?t=1756013880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/83686f52bdb7e2afff2a4d6403637190.mp4?t=1756013880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏内包含15+不同类型的的猫咪兵种<br>通过独特的配方合成升级召唤石，让其召唤出更加强力的猫猫兵！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174160/extras/36ada6f2b2eab5c80b0ee3b9abdb9f6a.avif?t=1756013880\" width=615 height=64 /></span